Anthony Martial is a great talent - Louis Saha
Media playback is not supported on this deviceFormer Manchester United striker Louis Saha says the Red Devils's new French forward Anthony Martial is "one of the most talented players in Europe".Martial, 19, signed from Monaco on transfer deadline day for Â£36m,making him the world's most expensive teenage footballer - a fee Saha describes as a "huge amount".However Saha, speaking at Soccerex, says he is "not surprised at all" to see Martial at Old Trafford, believing his compatriot has the speed to thrive in the Premier League.